request.description:
### Create a New Staff Member

This endpoint allows the creation of a new staff member.

#### Request Body

- `customFields` (array of objects) - Custom fields for the staff member.

    - `customField` (string) - Identifier for the custom field.

    - `k` (string) - Key for the custom field.

    - `v` (string) - Value for the custom field.

- `fullname` (string) - Full name of the staff member.

- `email` (string) - Email address of the staff member.

- `phone` (string) - Phone number of the staff member.

- `whatsAppPhone` (string) - WhatsApp phone number of the staff member.

- `role` (string) - Role identifier for the staff member.

- `workspaces` (array of strings) - Workspaces associated with the staff member.


#### Response Body (JSON Schema)

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "customFields": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "customField": { "type": "string" },
          "k": { "type": "string" },
          "v": { "type": "string" }
        }
      }
    },
    "fullname": { "type": "string" },
    "email": { "type": "string" },
    "phone": { "type": "string" },
    "whatsAppPhone": { "type": "string" },
    "workspaces": {
      "type": "array",
